Biocompatibles higher on Merrill buy note . Shares in Biocompatibles International Plc rocketed higher on Monday in further reaction to a Merrill Lynch buy note , issued on Friday , traders said . The shares were up 92 - 1 / 2p at 1247 - 1 / 2 by 1118 GMT . Merrill on Friday set an intermediate price target of 16 . 00 stg per share , saying the British healthcare technology group ' s profit outlook had improved since it embarked on a joint venture with specialist company Divysio in November . But traders were unsure whether the rise would continue . " It ' s a hairy stock , " one said . " Nobody knows whether it will carry on up to 16 pounds . " - - Paul Carrel , London newsroom + 44 171 542 5106 
